Package: scHelper
Title: Extension of the Seurat data class for single cell RNAseq analysis and visualisation
Version: 0.2.5
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Alex",
           family = "Thiery",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "alex.thiery@crick.ac.uk")
Description: scHelper is a library designed for single cell RNAseq analysis. This package is based off the Seurat data class object, and extends its functionality to assist with user friendly visualisation of quality control metrics, cell classification tools, and gene module identification (Antler - Delile et al. 2019).
Date:       2022-04-12
Type:       Package
License:    `use_mit_license()`
